## Wiki (Persistent Memory)

**Vault:** `~/WIKI/PROJECT-NAME/obsidian/`
**Compiler:** `~/WIKI/PROJECT-NAME/compiler/scripts/compile.py`

### Quick Reference
- **Start of session:** read `obsidian/index.md` — the master catalog of all wiki pages
- **Manual ingest:** tell the assistant "ingest" or "create wiki from daily" — it compiles pages directly
- **"remember this" / "note this":** create or update the relevant wiki page immediately
- **"lint the wiki":** `uv run --directory ~/WIKI/PROJECT-NAME/compiler python scripts/lint.py`

### Source Types
| Source | Nature | Lifecycle |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| `raw/` | Manual (devlog, articles, transcripts) | Immutable — never modified or deleted |
| `daily/` | Auto-generated (session summaries from hooks) | Ephemeral — deleted after compilation |

### Structure
```
obsidian/
├── index.md           ← READ FIRST. Master catalog.
├── log.md             ← Append-only activity log.
├── wiki-schema.md     ← Schema for the LLM agent.
├── daily/             ← Ephemeral session logs (deleted after compile).
├── raw/               ← Immutable source documents.
└── wiki/
    ├── concepts/      ← Atomic knowledge (patterns, bugs, features, ops).
    └── connections/   ← Cross-cutting links between topics.
```
